response.overview: In these digital times there is a niche revival happening with analog tape, vinyl, outboard gear and vintage mixing consoles. This is the introductory story that features three veteran audio engineers from the Pacific Northwest and one renegade engineer and studio owner in Nashville.
response.tagline: This is the introductory story that features three veteran audio engineers from the Pacific Northwest and one renegade engineer and studio owner in Nashville.
response.title: Analog Is Not Dead
